d in terms of Eichler\nintegrals, periods of the underlying elliptic curve defined by one of the\nassociated graph hypersurfaces, and powers of $2\\pi i$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 16:56:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-31"}
