 collision front of galaxies is compressed and becomes\ndenser. Our results imply that NGC 4567/4568 is in a very early stage of\ninteraction; otherwise, the molecular clouds in the filament would not yet\nfulfil the conditions necessary to trigger star formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 18:04:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
