or\nsolitons organized by EtoP connections only, multi-oscillation solitons are\nshown to be an integral part of the phenomenon of truncated homoclinic snaking.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2023 04:50:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-03"}
